1 The book of the genealogy of Jesus
Christ, the Son of David, the Son of
Abraham:
2 Abraham begot Isaac, Isaac begot
Jacob, and Jacob begot Judah and his
brothers.
3 Judah begot Perez and Zerah by
Tamar, Perez begot Hezron, and Hezron
begot Ram.
4 Ram begot Amminadab, Amminadab
begot Nahshon, and Nahshon begot
Salmon.
5 Salmon begot Boaz by Rahab, Boaz
begot Obed by Ruth, Obed begot Jesse,
6 and Jesse begot David the king. David
the king begot Solomon by her who had
been the wife of Uriah.MATTHEW 1
2
