9 Uzziah begot Jotham, Jotham begot
Ahaz, and Ahaz begot Hezekiah.
10 Hezekiah begot Manasseh, Manasseh
begot Amon, and Amon begot Josiah.
11 Josiah begot Jeconiah and his
brothers about the me they were
